  <h2>Carnegie Endowment Junior Fellows Program</h2>
<p>For students interested in a global affairs research internship at the Carnegie Institute.</p>
<ul>
<li>Requires UIC nomination</li>
<li>Eligibility: Must be eligible to work in U.S.; seniors or recent graduates</li>
